name: New Chinese Style Suit（新中式服饰）LoRa
description:
新中式服饰系列LoRa

以鲜花为形，百褶为型，重新定义新中式裙式。

推荐权重：0.6~1（裙摆褶皱会逐步变复杂）

在二次元、2.5D和写实模型下表现都非常好，希望大家多试试效果。

New Chinese-style clothing series LoRa

Taking flowers as the shape and folds as the form, redefining the new Chinese-style skirt.

Recommended weight: 0.6-1 (the pleats of the skirt will become gradually more complex)

It performs well in both 2D, 2.5D, and realistic models. We hope everyone can try it out and see the effect.
